OL,3,C'Crushed by a flawed system': More
OL,4,Cthan 2,000 still held under defunct UK
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FIPP (Indeterminate Sentences for
OL,8,FPublic Protection) sentences were
OL,9,Fsupposed to have been banned 13 years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FNow the stress of being left
OL,13,Flanguishing in prison, has been
OL,14,Frecognised in court for the first
OL,15,Ftime, ITV News West of England Report
OL,16,FSangita Lal explains
OL,18,FI've been speaking to IPP prisoners
OL,19,Ffor the last five years and they don't
OL,20,Fjust feel trapped in a flawed system,
OL,21,Fthey feel crushed by it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
