OL,3,C'Crushed by a flawed system': More
OL,4,Cthan 2,000 still held under defunct UK
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FCampaigners say there are still almost
OL,8,F2,500 stuck behind bars. The former
OL,9,FSupreme Court Judge Justice Lord Brown
OL,10,Fcalled it "the greatest single stain
OL,11,Fon our criminal justice system".
OL,13,FIt's hard to comprehend how the UK
OL,14,Fjustice system, which is built on
OL,15,Fcriminals serving time and being
OL,16,Freleased, is holding people in prison
OL,17,Funder a law that was abolished 23
OL,18,Fyears ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
