OL,3,C'Crushed by a flawed system': More
OL,4,Cthan 2,000 still held under defunct UK
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FIn 2022, after a three-year-long
OL,8,Finquiry, the Justice Select Committee
OL,9,Fcalled on the government to resentence
OL,10,Fall IPPs still in prison. The system
OL,11,Fwas described as 'irredeemably flawed'
OL,12,Fwhich was causing inmates to self harm.
OL,14,FIn response the then Conservative
OL,15,Fgovernment said it wasn't going to
OL,16,Fresentence IPPs, it was going to
OL,17,Freview the licensing conditions for
OL,18,Fthose who are released.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
