OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FIn 2021, I interviewed the sister of
OL,8,FWayne Bell, when he was 17 years old
OL,9,Fhe stole a bike in 2007.
OL,11,FHe's now detained under the mental
OL,12,Fhealth act, as he lives with
OL,13,Fschizophrenia. His sister Alana told
OL,14,Fme he believes he must have killed his
OL,15,Fdad, who's since died while he's been
OL,16,Fbehind bar, because he can't
OL,17,Funderstand why he's still in jail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
